# Forgot Password API Testing

### 1. Test Email Configuration
POST https://localhost:7139/api/Auth/test-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-test-email@gmail.com"
}

### 2. Request Password Reset
POST https://localhost:7139/api/Auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

### 3. Reset Password (API)
POST https://localhost:7139/api/Auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "token": "your-reset-token-from-email",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

### 4. Test Password Reset Page (Browser)
GET https://localhost:7139/api/Auth/reset-password?email=user@example.com&token=your-reset-token

### 5. Check Email Configuration
GET https://localhost:7139/api/Auth/email-config-test

### 6. Test Login with New Password
POST https://localhost:7139/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}